Blade Runner 2049 (2017)

Sci-Fi | Thriller
Thirty years after the events of the first film, a new blade runner, LAPD Officer K (Ryan Gosling), unearths a long-buried secret 

that has the potential to plunge what's left of society into chaos. K's discovery leads him on a quest to find Rick Deckard 

(Harrison Ford), a former LAPD blade runner who has been missing for 30 years.
Director: Denis Villeneuve
Stars: Harrison Ford, Ryan Gosling, Ana de Armas, Robin Wright
